Using summarize()
Creates one summary row per unique combination of groups:

penguins |&gt;
  select(species, island, body_mass_g) |&gt;
  filter(body_mass_g &gt; 4000) |&gt;
  group_by(species, island) |&gt;
  summarise(sd_mass = sd(body_mass_g, na.rm = TRUE))

